    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been a reliable daily driver. The engine and transmission are strong, and all scheduled maintenance has been performed on time. While the interior is clean and well-kept, there are some minor signs of wear consistent with its age, such as light scuffs on the upholstery and small exterior paint chips. All electronics and features, including the climate control and infotainment system, are fully functional. This is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "good",
