      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical attention and bodywork to be roadworthy again. The engine has a persistent knock, the transmission slips in higher gears, and there is visible rust along the rocker panels and wheel wells. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and many electronic features, including the AC, are currently non-functional. This car is best suited for a dedicated mechanic or as a source for parts.",
